This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with semantic dependency parsing, which is a task in natural language processing. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Additionally, the possibility of using the parser for image captioning tasks suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category of Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
